程序包 com.example.listycity

类 City

java.lang.Object
com.example.listycity.City
所有已实现的接口:
Comparable<City>
public class City extends Object implements Comparable<City>
Represents a Canadian city with a name and province/territory.

Implements Comparable so lists of cities can be sorted by name. equals / hashCode are provided so collections treat two City objects with the same name+province as the same logical city.
